<DOC><DOCNO> WSJ870416-0096 </DOCNO><HL> Who's News:U.S. Tobacco Co.</HL><DD> 04/16/87</DD><SO> WALL STREET JOURNAL (J)</SO><IN> WNEWS UBO </IN><DATELINE> U.S. TOBACCO CO. (Greenwich, Conn.)  </DATELINE><TEXT>    Per Erik Lindqvist,49 years old, was named to the new post of president of U.S.Tobacco International Inc., a unit. He remains senior vicepresident of the parent, a maker of smokeless tobaccoproducts. Joseph R. Taddeo was appointed to the new post ofvice president, industry relations, of the parent. His formerresponsibilities as vice president for internationalmarketing and sales of the company's tobacco products will beassumed by Mr. Lindqvist.</TEXT></DOC>